# Disabilities category traits

trait-deuteranopia-name = Deuteranopia
trait-deuteranopia-desc = You have red-green color blindness. The world looks a bit like a dog's painting. [Cosmetic - visual shader not yet implemented]

trait-ultra-vision-name = Ultraviolet Vision
trait-ultra-vision-desc = You can perceive ultraviolet light, giving your vision a faint tint. [Cosmetic - visual shader not yet implemented]

trait-arm-amputee-left-name = Left Arm Amputee
trait-arm-amputee-left-desc = Your left arm was amputated before your deployment. You cannot hold items in your left hand.

trait-arm-amputee-right-name = Right Arm Amputee
trait-arm-amputee-right-desc = Your right arm was amputated before your deployment. You cannot hold items in your right hand.

trait-dysgraphia-name = Dysgraphia
trait-dysgraphia-desc = You struggle with writing. You are unable to write on paper or other documents.
